CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. B7 reads: "4. Harlene Williams,...winner of a grand prize, the Proctor Toaster, and Mrs. Jean...of 324 Burrows St., winner of a Proctor Ironing Board, proudly...prizes."
TitMainTitle: Booth featuring gas appliances at trade show, with WAMO disc jockey John "Sir Walter" Christian and Daisy Lampkin and two women at microphone on stage and two women on floor with toaster and ironing board
